title: The Hometown Hero & The Homecoming Queen
description: In this Dateline classic, an Olympic athlete and a homecoming queen share a life in the charming suburb of Oxnard, California until gunshots are fired in their backyard on a late summer night in 2009. Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on April 1, 2016.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
